            <h2>Popular AWS Services</h2>
            <ul>
                <li><strong>EC2:</strong> Virtual servers in the cloud</li>
                <li><strong>S3:</strong> Scalable object storage for any type of data</li>
                <li><strong>RDS:</strong> Managed relational databases like MySQL, PostgreSQL</li>
